correctly scoped, and independently reproducible: the docstring is now
factually accurate and the regression test genuinely exercises a
middleware-raised exception (not a route handler); the two new CSRF
tests genuinely assert DB-level non-side-effects, not just status
codes. Full suite green (211/211), ruff and mypy clean. Task 3D is
cleared for the required adversarial review.

